videos.description: Zion Williamson posts up the defender and goes right around him for an early two points for Duke.
videos.headline: Zion powers through D for 2 points

videos.description: Zion Williamson is wide open for the 3-pointer as Duke grabs the lead early.
videos.headline: Zion hits early 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke junior Jack White stuffs two shots at the rim in less than 10 seconds vs. Wake Forest.
videos.headline: White records two blocks in 10 seconds

videos.description: Tre Jones throws it up to Zion Williamson who throws down a violent two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Zion throws down monster alley-oop

videos.description: Zion Williamson attempts a one-handed slam, but comes up with a rare miss.
videos.headline: Zion misses one-handed slam

videos.description: During Duke's pregame warmups, Duke star Zion Williamson gets hit in the face with a basketball.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Misc (Zion gets hit in face during warmups) 2019/01/08 SC

videos.headline: Zion gets hit in face during warmups

videos.description: RJ Barrett finds Zion Williamson soaring over the defense for another Duke alley-oop.
videos.headline: Zion hits another big alley-oop

videos.description: With a layup late in the second half, Zion Williamson sets a new career high in points with 30.
videos.headline: Zion hits career-high 30 points with layup

videos.description: RJ Barrett crosses his defender up and puts him on the ground as he drains the easy 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Barrett breaks defender's ankles

videos.description: Zion Williamson discusses how Duke's defense led to offensive opportunities, his close relationship with RJ Barrett and missing a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Zion talks close relationship with Barrett) 2019/01/08

videos.headline: Zion talks close relationship with Barrett

videos.description: ESPN NBA Draft analyst Mike Schmitz reflects on Zion Williamson's shooting game, in which he said being a non-shooter in high school is his "biggest weakness."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Schmitz: Shooting is Zion’s ‘biggest weakness’) 2018/1/8 SC ESHEET

videos.headline: Schmitz: Shooting is Zion's 'biggest weakness'
